  "title": "Art teacher",
  "description": "<p>Planning lessons on art in accordance with student’s learning objectives.</p><p></p><p>Preparing the classroom by gathering and setting up equipment.</p><p></p><p>Developing student’s drawing, coloring, and painting techniques.</p><p></p><p>Providing instruction on the use media such as graphite and charcoal pencils, as well as oil, acrylic, and watercolor paint.</p><p></p><p>Assigning and grading project and examinations.</p><p></p><p>Recording and reporting on student’s progress.</p><p></p><p>Ensuring that the classroom is clean after each lesson.</p><p></p><p>Monitoring inventory and sourcing art supplies, as needed.</p><p></p><p>Attending faculty and parent- teacher meetings.</p><p></p>",
